The paper deals with the problem of online clustering, which is a topic in machine learning and data science. Specifically, it focuses on the $k$-means objective, which is a popular clustering algorithm. Therefore, the most likely category is cs.LG (Machine Learning), followed by cs.DS (Data Structures and Algorithms) and cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence). The paper also involves information theory (cs.IT) and signal processing (cs.SI) in its analysis.
